Don’t feel guilty at all.

01:15:33.827 --> 01:15:36.117
Otherwise I would not come here.

01:15:36.117 --> 01:15:43.337
The ones who have harmed you are guilty.

01:15:51.078 --> 01:15:59.440
Seeker: What is your capacity and our capacity
to hate the devils.

01:15:59.465 --> 01:16:03.277
Most religions preached that we should not
be angry.

01:16:03.277 --> 01:16:08.867
Shri Mataji: You should not be angry, but
with Devils?

01:16:08.892 --> 01:16:12.143
You run away from them.

01:16:12.238 --> 01:16:13.238
Let me handle them.

01:16:13.262 --> 01:16:14.496
You don´t worry.

01:16:14.521 --> 01:16:16.115
You just don’t worry about them.

01:16:16.139 --> 01:16:18.139
All right?

01:16:18.153 --> 01:16:19.443
It’s my job.

