01:17:54.767 --> 01:17:58.057
I’ll make you the masters.

01:17:58.057 --> 01:18:00.307
It’s Love.

01:18:00.307 --> 01:18:01.467
It cannot harm.

01:18:01.467 --> 01:18:03.067
It’s your Mother.

01:18:03.067 --> 01:18:07.987
That’s the only Mother you have and you
are the only child.

01:18:07.987 --> 01:18:10.297
How can your Kundalini trouble you?

01:18:10.297 --> 01:18:13.448
She is just waiting for the moment to give
you realization.

01:18:13.473 --> 01:18:23.792
She loves you the most of all.

01:18:24.521 --> 01:18:32.700
And you cannot activate it, it just spontaneously
rises.

01:18:32.725 --> 01:18:37.347
I was myself amazed to read some books on
Kundalini.

01:18:37.372 --> 01:18:39.479
I said these people don’t know what Kundalini
is.

01:18:39.504 --> 01:18:40.552
They tell lies

01:18:40.553 --> 01:18:41.626
They’re liars.

01:18:41.651 --> 01:18:47.566
They are cheats writing such big books about
Kundalini without knowing a word, without

01:18:47.591 --> 01:18:48.801
having any authority.

01:18:48.826 --> 01:18:50.896
You have to have Divine Authority, isn’t
it?

01:18:50.921 --> 01:18:54.591
You cannot get it in a Theological college
or any place you go to.

01:18:54.615 --> 01:18:55.414
You can not.

01:18:55.439 --> 01:18:57.641
Its a Divine Authority you must have.

01:19:03.502 --> 01:19:06.852
Seeker: Should we love our enemies as well?

01:19:06.877 --> 01:19:08.962
Shri Mataji: First of all you love yourself
and your friends.

01:19:08.987 --> 01:19:17.267
Then we can talk of enemies.

01:19:17.816 --> 01:19:20.702
